eld-27","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#keyboard","content":"Stepper buttons are real buttons and follow standard button keyboard activation. Use &#x2A;*`incrementAriaLabel`*&#x2A; and &#x2A;*`decrementAriaLabel`** when the default labels are not enough in your locale or UI."},"403":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-28","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#aria-and-labeling","content":"The input is associated with the visible label and optional description and error content for assistive technologies."},"404":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-29","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#aria-and-labeling","content":"Invalid and required states are exposed to assistive technologies when you use `isInvalid`, `errorMessage`, and `isRequired`."},"405":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-30","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#aria-and-labeling","content":"Set &#x2A;*`isWheelDisabled`** if the value should not change when the user scrolls with a pointer wheel while the field is focused."},"406":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-31","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#best-practices","content":"Pair &#x2A;*`isInvalid`*&#x2A; with &#x2A;*`errorMessage`** so users get both visual and programmatic feedback."},"407":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-32","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#best-practices","content":"Remember valid steps start from &#x2A;*`minValue`**."},"408":{"id":"/docs/components/number-field-33","page_id":"/docs/components/number-field","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/number-field#best-practices","content":"Use &#x2A;*`isDisabled`*&#x2