sed"],[804,"**Default:** When `formatValue` is not provided, the tooltip uses a formatter that reads the data point’s `y` property (same as the chart's default Y accessor), converts it to a string, and returns an empty string for null. This is correct for the default `DataPoint` shape (`{ x, y }`)."],[910,"**Default**: `'bottom'`"],[902,"**Default**: `'vertical'`"],[906,"**Default**: `500`"],[908,"**Default**: `700`"],[917,"**Default**: `true`"],[919,"**Default**: `true`"],[921,"**Default**: `true`"],[923,"**Default**: `true`"],[925,"**Default**: `true`"],[927,"**Default**: `true`"],[951,"**Default**: `true`"],[885,"**Design system alignment**: 8px border radius, 12px bar width (1.5 GU), consistent spacing"],[293,"**DOM Output:**"],[117,"**errorMessage**: Displays validation error text below the group"],[342,"**Escape**: Closes menu"],[565,"**Escape**: Closes the popover"],[238,"**Events**: `onClick`, `onMouseOver`, `onFocus`, etc."],[309,"**Fallback content**: Provide placeholder content for loading states"],[297,"**Faster Rendering**: Browser optimizations for `<use>` elements"],[165,"**Field wrapper composition**: Designed to sit inside TextField, NumberField, DateField, or Select as the main field UI"],[172,"**FieldError** (optional) — Rendered when `errorMessage` is provided. Rendered below the Group, above the description. Associated with the field for accessibility."],[282,"**First Request**: When an icon is first encountered, it triggers an asynchronous fetch from the CDN"],[230,"**Flexible sizing**: Support for `width` and `height` props"],[161,"**Focus delegation**: Tracks focus from any focusable child (input, button) via `data-focus-within` and `data-focus-visible`"],[285,"**Full SVG Rendering**: Each icon instance renders as a complete SVG element with all path data"],[965,"**Group gap**: Minimum 24px between bar groups"],[171,"**Group** — The visual frame. Exposes `data-focus-within`, `data-focus-visible`, `data-disabled`, and `data-invalid`. All focusable children (input, button, etc.) live inside this Group."],[977,"**Grouped rendering**: Bars are rendered in SVG `<Group>` elements for logical organization"],[401,"**Home** / **End**: jump to `minValue` or `maxValue` when those props are set"],[341,"**Home/End**: Jump to first/last item"],[564,"**Home/End**: Jump to first/last option"],[980,"**Horizontal charts**: Vertical scrolling when many categories exceed container height"],[1012,"**Horizontal Multi-Series**: Grouped horizontal bars"],[969,"**Horizontal scrolling**: When data points exceed available width, the chart becomes horizontally scrollable"],[1011,"**Horizontal Single Series**: Horizontal orientation"],[1059,"**HTML Elements:** When using `as=\"button\"`, TypeScript enforces button-specific props like `type`, `disabled`, and `onClick`."],[1045,"**Important**: Since `Flex` and `Grid` extend `Box`, prefer them for layouts. Use `Box` only when you need a non-flex, non-grid container."],[260,"**Important**: When you supply a `className`, you make a commitment to take over all styling of the component as it will remove the standard class names. Use data attributes for targeted styling instead."],[300,"**Initial Flash**: Brief moment where icons appear/disappear during sprite injection"],[1027,"**Inputs.** Wire `parentRef` to the scroll container and `xAxisRef` / `yAxisRef` to the axis groups. Optionally pass `xLabelsOrientation` (`'auto'` | `'horizontal'` | `'vertical'`, default `'auto'`) to force the category-label layout; `'auto'` rotates labels vertical when the visible width can't fit the horizontal-tick footprint plus the Y-axis width."],[886,"**Interactive tooltips**: Hover to see exact values, with smart positioning and scroll-awareness"],[116,"**isInvalid**: Shows error state styling"],[115,"**isRequired**: Marks the group as required with visual indicator"],[972,"**Keyboard navigation**: Bar groups are keyboard accessible with `tabIndex={0}` and `role=\"group\"`"],[601,"**Label, description, error**: Optional label, helper text, and error message with proper accessibility"],[162,"**Label, description, error**: Optional Label, helper Text, and FieldError with proper accessibility association"],[170,"**Label** (optional) — Rendered when `label` is provided. Shows a required indicator (asterisk)."],[1005,"**Limit data points**: Consider pagination or filtering for very large datasets (>100 points)"],[560,"**List Items:** `data-hovered`, `data-focused`, `data-pressed`, `data-selected`, `data-disabled`, `data-selection-mode`"],[296,"**Lower Memory Usage**: Especially beneficial with many repeated icons"],[967,"**Margins**: 20px top/right, 60px bottom/left for axes and labels"],[334,"**Menu Items:** `data-hovered`, `data-focused`, `data-pressed`, `data-selected`, `data-disabled`"],[313,"**Minimize icon sets**: Only load icons that are actually used"],[971,"**Minimum spacing**: Group gaps never fall below 24px, triggering scroll instead"],[1010,"**Multi-Series**: Grouped bars with legend"],[604,"**Multiline**: Set `multiline` to render a textarea instead of a single-line input"],[799,"**Multiple series**: Shows all series that have a datum at the hovered X position in a single tooltip."],[307,"**Network connectivity**: Verify CDN is accessible"],[961,"**Note**: RTL support is currently in active development. Axis rendering and tick mark spacing are being refined."],[228,"**On-demand loading**: Icons are loaded asynchronously from CDN only when needed"],[911,"**Options**: `'top'` | `'bottom'`"],[903,"**Options**: `'vertical'` | `'horizontal'`"],[1028,"**Outputs.** The hook returns `margin`, `chartWidth`, `chartHeight`, `xLabelsVertical`, `scrollLeft` / `scrollTop`, and `yAxisRect` for the chart to consume. Width and height are sized to whichever is larger — the visible slot or the room the rendered labels need — so the chart grows past the viewport and the parent scrolls when labels demand more space."],[400,"**Page Up** / **Page Down**: larger increase or decrease when supported"],[294,"**Performance Benefits:**"],[335,"**Popover:** `data-entering`, `data-exiting`"],[559,"**Popover:** `data-entering`, `data-exiting`"],[311,"**Preload common icons**: Consider preloading frequently used icons"],[304,"**Provide fallback content** for critical icons to handle loading states"],[469,"**Radio Button:** `data-selected`, `data-hovered`, `data-pressed`, `data-focused`, `data-disabled`"],[468,"**RadioGroup Container:** `data-invalid`, `data-disabled`, `data-required`, `data-readonly`, `data-orientation`"],[606,"**React Aria integration**: Built on React Aria TextField for accessibility and behavior"],[164,"**React Aria integration**: Uses Provider pattern so nested elements stay in sync with the frame"],[1082,"**Recommended default**: Use Flex for most layouts. Since it extends Box, you get all Box capabilities without needing to nest components."],[295,"**Reduced DOM Size**: Path data stored once instead of duplicated"],[290,"**Reference Rendering**: Each icon renders as a lightweight `<use>` element that references the sprite"],[163,"**Required indicator**: Shows asterisk next to label when the field is required"],[884,"**Responsive behavior**: Auto-sizing with horizontal scrolling for many data points, sticky axes"],[978,"**Responsive sizing**: `useParentSize` hook provides efficient resize detection with debouncing (15ms)"],[1014,"**RTL Multi-Series*&#x2A;: Multi-series chart in RTL &#x2A;(in development)*"],[889,"**RTL support*&#x2A;: Full right-to-left layout support for international audiences &#x2A;(in development)*"],[976,"**Scales**: VisX's `scaleBand` and `scaleLinear` for efficient coordinate mapping"],[973,"**Screen reader support**: Semantic HTML structure with proper ARIA attributes"],[522,"**SegmentedController Container:** `data-disabled`"],[523,"**SegmentedControllerItem:** `data-selected`, `data-hovered`, `data-pressed`, `data-focus-visible`, `data-disabled`"],[556,"**Select Container:** `data-invalid`, `data-disabled`, `data-required`, `data-focused`"],[558,"**Select Value:** `data-placeholder`"],[800,"**Series matching**: Rows are built from `series` by matching `series[].id` to keys in `tooltipData.datumByKey` (from visx at the hovered X)."],[125,"**Shift + Tab**: Moves focus to the previous checkbox"],[1007,"**Simplify tooltips**: If tooltips are complex, consider using simpler content or disabling them"],[882,"**Single and multi-series support**: Display one or multiple data series with grouped bars"],[1009,"**Single Series**: Basic vertical bar chart"],[568,"**Space** (in multi-select): Toggle selection of focused item"],[474,"**Space**: Select the focused radio button"],[124,"**Space**: Toggles the focused checkbox"],[337,"**Space/Enter**: Opens menu and activates items"],[562,"**Space/Enter**: Opens the popover and focuses the selected item"],[526,"**Space/Enter**: Select the focused segment"],[289,"**Sprite Sheet Creation**: A hidden SVG sprite sheet is automatically injected into the DOM containing symbol definitions"],[299,"**SSR Limitation**: Sprite references render empty until client-side hydration"],[981,"**Sticky axes**: Positioned absolutely to remain visible during scroll"],[970,"**Sticky y-axis**: The y-axis remains visible during horizontal scroll"],[239,"**Styling**: `className`, `style`, `data-*` attributes"],[283,"**SVG Parsing**: The fetched SVG string is parsed into a React element using `@bento/svg-parser`"],[343,"**Tab**: Closes menu and moves to next element"],[566,"**Tab**: Moves focus to the next focusable element"],[123,"**Tab**: Moves focus to the next/previous checkbox"],[471,"**Tab**: Moves focus to/from the radio group"],[524,"**Tab**: Moves focus to/from the segmented controller"],[173,"**Text** (optional) — Description block rendered when `description` is provided."],[985,"**Tooltips** use absolute positioning and scroll-aware calculations for accurate placement"],[974,"**Tooltips**: Show on both hover and focus for keyboard users"],[298,"*